snippet.title: Helldivers 2 - Announce Trailer | PS5 & PC Games
snippet.description:
It’s time to take out the alien trash!
Join the Helldivers to fight for freedom across a hostile galaxy in third-person co-op shooter operations. Developed by Arrowhead Game Studios. Coming soon to PlayStation 5 and PC

Enlist today at: https://www.playstation.com/helldivers2

Internet connection required. Paid PS Plus subscription required to play on PS5; fees recur until cancelled. Age restrictions apply. Full terms: play.st/psplus-usageterms

#PlayStationShowcase #PlayStation #ps5 #ps5games
